## Datagram vs Stream

- **Stream**: Byte stream, no message boundaries
- **Datagram**: Message oriented, each send/recv is complete message

## Use Cases

1. **Logging**: Send log messages to syslog-style listener
2. **Notifications**: One-way event notifications
3. **Request-reply**: Simple RPC pattern

